    <text id="B0247T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Terry, in McDonnell's absence, asks Jackson to submit paperwork related to the
                    renting of space for schoolrooms.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau of Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands,<lb/>Head Quarters 9th District
                    Department of the Potomac
                    <name type="recipient">Mr. <abbr expan="Thomas">Thos.</abbr> P.
                        Jackson<lb/>Agent<lb/>Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-05-25">May 25th 1867.</date>
                        <name type="place">Winchester, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>In <abbr expan="Captain">Capt.</abbr> McDonnell's temporary absence, I <orig
                        reg="enclose">inclose</orig> new sets - <unclear>vouchers</unclear> for
                    schoolroom rest at Staunton, presuming that if new Lease is approved, the old
                    one will be rescinded, from date of new one, please state if that is the
                    intention. As a precautionary measure, please send the other set of vouchers
                    receipted as well as them and return them by first mail.</p>

                <p>If the schools are to be closed all summer, I doubt if it will be thought best to
                    pay $25 per month for an empty room till Fall.</p>

                <p>Please give my regards to Mr. Tukey and family.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>Addn F. Terry<lb/><abbr expan="clerk">clk</abbr></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
